name: CDM-3.1
dataExportConf:
<dataExportConfig cases-per-file='70000'>
<outputFile name='demographic.csv' source='demographic'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Birth Date' colName='BIRTH_DATE' deid='birthday' />
	    <field name='Birth Time' colName='BIRTH_TIME' />
	    <field name='Sex' colName='SEX' />
	    <field name='Sexual Orientation' colName='SEXUAL_ORIENTATION' />
	    <field name='Gender Identity' colName='GENDER_IDENTITY' />
	    <field name='Hispanic' colName='HISPANIC' />
	    <field name='Race' colName='RACE'/>
	    <field name='Biobank Flag' colName='BIOBANK_FLAG'/>
	    <field name='Raw Sex' colName='RAW_SEX'/>
	    <field name='Raw Sexual Orientation' colName='RAW_SEXUAL_ORIENTATION'/>
	    <field name='Raw Gender Identity' colName='RAW_GENDER_IDENTITY'/>
	    <field name='Raw Hispanic' colName='RAW_HISPANIC'/>
	    <field name='Raw Race' colName='RAW_RACE'/>	    
    </custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
<outputFile name='enrollment.csv' source='enrollment'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Enr State Date' colName='ENR_START_DATE' />
	    <field name='Enr End Date' colName='ENR_END_DATE' />
	    <field name='Chart' colName='CHART' />
	    <field name='Enr Basis' colName='ENR_BASIS' />
	</custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
<outputFile name='encounter.csv' source='encounter'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Endcounter Id' colName='ENCOUNTERID' />
	    <field name='Admit Date' colName='ADMIT_DATE' />
	    <field name='Admit Time' colName='ADMIT_TIME' />
	    <field name='Discharge Date' colName='DISCHARGE_DATE' />
	    <field name='Discharge Time' colName='DISCHARGE_TIME' />
	    <field name='Provider Id' colName='PROVIDERID' />
	    <field name='Facility Location' colName='FACILITY_LOCATION' />
	    <field name='Enc Type' colName='ENC_TYPE' />
	    <field name='Facility Id' colName='FACILITYID' />	    
	    <field name='Discharge Disposition' colName='DISCHARGE_DISPOSITION' />
	    <field name='Discharge Status' colName='DISCHARGE_STATUS' />
	    <field name='DRG' colName='DRG' />
	    <field name='DRG Type' colName='DRG_TYPE' />
	    <field name='Admitting Source' colName='ADMITTING_SOURCE' />
	    <field name='Raw Site Id' colName='RAW_SITEID' />
	    <field name='Raw Enc Type' colName='RAW_ENC_TYPE' />
	    <field name='Raw Discharge Disposition' colName='RAW_DISCHARGE_DISPOSITION' />
	    <field name='Raw Discharge Status' colName='RAW_DISCHARGE_STATUS' />
	    <field name='Raw DRG Type' colName='RAW_DRG_TYPE' />
	    <field name='Raw Admitting Source' colName='RAW_ADMITTING_SOURCE' />
	</custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
<outputFile name='diagnosis.csv' source='diagnosis'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Encounter Id' colName='ENCOUNTERID' />
	    <field name='Enc Type' colName='ENC_TYPE' />
	    <field name='Admit Date' colName='ADMIT_DATE' />
	    <field name='Provider Id' colName='PROVIDERID' />
	    <field name='DX' colName='DX' />
	    <field name='DX Type' colName='DX_TYPE' />
	    <field name='DX Source' colName='DX_SOURCE' />
	    <field name='DX Origin' colName='DX_ORIGIN' />
	    <field name='PDX' colName='PDX' />
	    <field name='Raw DX' colName='RAW_DX' />
	    <field name='Raw DX Type' colName='RAW_DX_TYPE' />
	    <field name='Raw DX Source' colName='RAW_DX_SOURCE' />
	    <field name='Raw PDX' colName='RAW_PDX' />
	</custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
<outputFile name='procedures.csv' source='procedures'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Procedures Id' colName='PROCEDURESID' />
	    <field name='Encounter Id' colName='ENCOUNTERID' />
	    <field name='Enc Type' colName='ENC_TYPE' />
	    <field name='Admit Date' colName='ADMIT_DATE' />
	    <field name='Provider Id' colName='PROVIDERID' />
	    <field name='PX Date' colName='PX_DATE' />
	    <field name='PX' colName='PX' />
	    <field name='PX Type' colName='PX_TYPE' />
	    <field name='PX Source' colName='PX_SOURCE' />
	    <field name='Raw PX' colName='RAW_PX' />
	    <field name='Raw PX Type' colName='RAW_PX_TYPE' />
	</custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
<outputFile name='vital.csv' source='vital'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Encounter Id' colName='ENCOUNTERID' />
	    <field name='Measure Date' colName='MEASURE_DATE' />
	    <field name='Measure Time' colName='MEASURE_TIME' />
	    <field name='Vital Source' colName='VITAL_SOURCE' />
	    <field name='HT' colName='HT' />
	    <field name='WT' colName='WT' />
	    <field name='Diastolic' colName='DIASTOLIC' />
	    <field name='Systolic' colName='SYSTOLIC' />
	    <field name='Original BMI' colName='ORIGINAL_BMI' />
	    <field name='BP Position' colName='BP_POSITION' />
	    <field name='Smoking' colName='SMOKING' />
	    <field name='Tobacco' colName='TOBACCO' />
	    <field name='Tobacco Type' colName='TOBACCO_TYPE' />
	    <field name='Raw Vital Source' colName='RAW_VITAL_SOURCE' />
	    <field name='Raw Diastolic' colName='RAW_DIASTOLIC' />
	    <field name='Raw Systolic' colName='RAW_SYSTOLIC' />
	    <field name='Raw BP Position' colName='RAW_BP_POSITION' />
	    <field name='Raw Smoking' colName='RAW_SMOKING' />
	    <field name='Raw Tobacco' colName='RAW_TOBACCO' />
	    <field name='Raw Tobacco Type' colName='RAW_TOBACCO_TYPE' />
	</custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
<outputFile name='dispensing.csv' source='dispensing'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Prescribing Id' colName='PRESCRIBINGID' />
	    <field name='Dispense Date' colName='DISPENSE_DATE' />
	    <field name='NDC' colName='NDC' />
	    <field name='Dispense Sup' colName='DISPENSE_SUP' />
	    <field name='Dispense Amt' colName='DISPENSE_AMT' />
	    <field name='Raw NDC' colName='RAW_NDC' />
	</custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
<outputFile name='lab_result_cm.csv' source='lab_result_cm'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Encounter Id' colName='ENCOUNTERID' />
	    <field name='Lab Name' colName='LAB_NAME' />
	    <field name='Specimen Source' colName='SPECIMEN_SOURCE' />
	    <field name='Lab LOINC' colName='LAB_LOINC' />
	    <field name='Priority' colName='PRIORITY' />
	    <field name='Result Loc' colName='RESULT_LOC' />
	    <field name='Lab PX' colName='LAB_PX' />
	    <field name='Lab PX Type' colName='LAB_PX_TYPE' />
	    <field name='Lab Order Date' colName='LAB_ORDER_DATE' />
	    <field name='Specimen Date' colName='SPECIMEN_DATE' />
	    <field name='Specimen Time' colName='SPECIMEN_TIME' />
	    <field name='Result Date' colName='RESULT_DATE' />
	    <field name='Result Time' colName='RESULT_TIME' />
	    <field name='Result Qual' colName='RESULT_QUAL' />
	    <field name='Result Num' colName='RESULT_NUM' />
	    <field name='Result Modifier' colName='RESULT_MODIFIER' />
	    <field name='Result Unit' colName='RESULT_UNIT' />
	    <field name='Norm Range Low' colName='NORM_RANGE_LOW' />
	    <field name='Norm Modifier Low' colName='NORM_MODIFIER_LOW' />
	    <field name='Norm Range High' colName='NORM_RANGE_HIGH' />
	    <field name='Norm Modifier High' colName='NORM_MODIFIER_HIGH' />
	    <field name='Abn Ind' colName='ABN_IND' />
	    <field name='Raw Lab Name' colName='RAW_LAB_NAME' />
	    <field name='Raw Lab Code' colName='RAW_LAB_CODE' />
	    <field name='Raw Panel' colName='RAW_PANEL' />
	    <field name='Raw Result' colName='RAW_RESULT' />
	    <field name='Raw Unit' colName='RAW_UNIT' />
	    <field name='Raw Order Dept' colName='RAW_ORDER_DEPT' />
	    <field name='Raw Facility Code' colName='RAW_FACILITY_CODE' />
	</custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
<outputFile name='condition.csv' source='condition'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Encounter Id' colName='ENCOUNTERID' />
	    <field name='Report Date' colName='REPORT_DATE' />
	    <field name='Resolve Date' colName='RESOLVE_DATE' />
	    <field name='Onset Date' colName='ONSET_DATE' />
	    <field name='Condition Status' colName='CONDITION_STATUS' />
	    <field name='Condition' colName='CONDITION' />
	    <field name='Condition Type' colName='CONDITION_TYPE' />
	    <field name='Condition Source' colName='CONDITION_SOURCE' />
	    <field name='Raw Condition Status' colName='RAW_CONDITION_STATUS' />
	    <field name='Raw Condition' colName='RAW_CONDITION' />
	    <field name='Raw Condition Type' colName='RAW_CONDITION_TYPE' />
	    <field name='Raw Condition Source' colName='RAW_CONDITION_SOURCE' />
	</custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
<outputFile name='pro_cm.csv' source='pro_cm'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Encounter Id' colName='ENCOUNTERID' />
	    <field name='PRO Item' colName='PRO_ITEM' />
	    <field name='PRO LOINC' colName='PRO_LOINC' />
	    <field name='PRO Date' colName='PRO_DATE' />
	    <field name='PRO Time' colName='PRO_TIME' />
	    <field name='PRO Response' colName='PRO_RESPONSE' />

	</custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
<outputFile name='prescribing.csv' source='prescribing'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Prescribing Id' colName='PRESCRIBINGID' />
	    <field name='Encounter Id' colName='ENCOUNTERID' />
	    <field name='RX Provider Id' colName='RX_PROVIDERID' />
	    <field name='RX Order Date' colName='RX_ORDER_DATE' />
	    <field name='RX Order Time' colName='RX_ORDER_TIME' />
	    <field name='RX Start Date' colName='RX_START_DATE' />

	    <field name='RX Quantity' colName='RX_QUANTITY' />

	    <field name='RX Refills' colName='RX_REFILLS' />

	</custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
<outputFile name='death.csv' source='death'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Death Date' colName='DEATH_DATE' />
	    <field name='Death Date Impute' colName='DEATH_DATE_IMPUTE' />
	    <field name='Death Source' colName='DEATH_SOURCE' />
	    <field name='Death Match Confidence' colName='DEATH_MATCH_CONFIDENCE' />
	</custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
<outputFile name='death_cause.csv' source='death_cause'>
	<idColumn>PATID</idColumn>
    <custom-column-set>
	    <field name='Death Cause' colName='DEATH_CAUSE' />
	    <field name='Death Cause Code' colName='DEATH_CAUSE_CODE' />
	    <field name='Death Cause Type' colName='DEATH_CAUSE_TYPE' />
	    <field name='Death Cause Source' colName='DEATH_CAUSE_SOURCE' />

	</custom-column-set>
</outputFile>
</dataExportConfig>
